lyrics:
[Verse]
Step into a world where magic’s in the air
Where Miss Bea Haven reigns with flair
In Palm Springs’ heart, where dreams come alive
With every laugh and smile, we thrive

[Chorus]
The magic of Miss Bea Haven, in every hue
With whimsical wigs and costumes so true
Enchanting hearts with her kooky charm
In the land of joy, where dreams disarm
